<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.8.1">
<l>māṟṟa muḷavā kiluñcol luvaṉmakkaḷ</l>
<l>tōṟṟak kuḻitōṟ ṟuvippāy koleṉṟiṉṉam</l>
<l>āṟṟaṅ karaivāḻ marampō lañcukiṉṟēṉ</l>
<l>nāṟṟañ cuvaiyū ṟoliyā kiyanampī.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if there are objections, I will speak:</l>
<l>Like a tree living at the edge of the river, I dread</l>
<l>‘Will you make me be created again in the pit which creates children?’</l>
<l>Noble [lord] who is scent, taste, touch, and sound.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
